Package: simulatr
Title: Simulation of Multivariate Linear Model Data
Version: 0.1
Authors@R: person("Raju", "Rimal", email = "raju.rimal@nmbu.no",
                  role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: This package can be used to simulate multivariate linear model data. The package also consist of function to create plots for the simulation objects. It can be a handy tool for model comparison, testing and many other purposes.
Depends:
    R (>= 3.1.0)
License: GPL-3
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
RoxygenNote: 5.0.1
Imports: ggplot2, gridExtra, data.table
Suggests: testthat
